<div dir="ltr"><div>you can use a shared ( i.e. NFS ) folder with this app, or provide a full PATH to it.<br></div><div>ex: </div><div>$mpirun -np 2 -hostfile hostfile  /home/user/app</div><br><div class="gmail_quote">2009/9/15 Dominik Táborský <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:bremby@seznam.cz">bremby@seznam.cz</a>&gt;</span><br>
